---
title: Carb Smart Loaded Bunless Beef Burgers with Arugula and Spinach
description: Any night can be burger night, but sometimes we decide to leave the bun behind! Start with a nutritious salad base then add the juicy all-beef patties and pile on the pickles, crispy shallots and creamy Dijonnaise.

Carb Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.
